File: platform/mcp-server/src/browser-tools/analyze-site/index.ts lines 825-1012.

Network capture is enabled at line 827 and disabled at line 952. If `getNetworkRequests` at line 943 throws, line 952 is never reached. The finally block (line 1005) only closes the tab.

Fix: Move `disableNetworkCapture` into the finally block before the closeTab call (line 1007-1011). Wrap it in its own try-catch so a failure to disable capture doesn't prevent tab cleanup:

```typescript
finally {
  try {
    await dispatchToExtension(state, 'browser.disableNetworkCapture', { tabId });
  } catch {
    // Best-effort cleanup
  }
  try {
    await dispatchToExtension(state, 'browser.closeTab', { tabId });
  } catch {
    // Best-effort cleanup
  }
}
```

Also remove the `disableNetworkCapture` call at line 952 since it's now in the finally block. Keep the getNetworkRequests call at its current location.
